<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Access Denied | ACCELA</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Share+Tech+Mono&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
      background-color: #000;
      color: #ff70a6;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 4rem 1rem 2rem;
      background-size: cover;
      background-repeat: no-repeat;
      background-attachment: fixed;
      background-position: center;
      background-blend-mode: overlay;
      backdrop-filter: blur(1px);
    }

  
    h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      animation: glitch 2s infinite;
      text-shadow: 0 0 4px #ff70a6, 0 0 10px #ff70a6;
    }

    p {
      margin-top: 1rem;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      animation: flicker 1.5s infinite;
    }

    .lain-img {
      margin-top: 2rem;
      max-width: 320px;
      border: 2px solid #ff70a6;
      animation: glitch 3s infinite;
    }

    .btn {
      margin-top: 3rem;
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
      background: transparent;
      color: #ff70a6;
      border: 1px solid #ff70a6;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 1rem;
      transition: 0.3s ease;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      background: #ff70a6;
      color: #000;
    }

    @keyframes glitch {
      0% { transform: translate(0); }
      20% { transform: translate(-2px, 1px); }
      40% { transform: translate(2px, -1px); }
      60% { transform: translate(-1px, 2px); }
      80% { transform: translate(1px, -2px); }
      100% { transform: translate(0); }
    }

    @keyframes flicker {
      0%, 100% { opacity: 0.1; }
      50% { opacity: 0.8; }
      75% { opacity: 0.3; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  
  <h1>⚠ ACCESS DENIED — YOU'VE ENTERED THE LAIN ZONE ⚠</h1>
  <p>This network does not recognize your existence.</p>
  <img class="lain-img" src="https://files.catbox.moe/s13m8w.gif" alt="Lain watching">
  <p>Return to <a class="btn" href="/">safety</a></p>
</body>
</html>
